    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The 6 not-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 for a Class II device. The CFD model is assessed as credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions within the defined COU. The primary hemolysis validation result demonstrates mean RHI error of 9.4% against FDA benchmark data. The pressure-head validation confirms flow-field fidelity. The credibility assessment team accepts the model for the stated COU and decision context.",
